# A Makefile for Developing Containerized LaTeX Technical Documents
https://arxiv.org/abs/2005.12660

# Requirements
POSIX Shell & Utilities
Git
Docker
NVIDIA Container Toolkit (Optional)

# Download
git clone https://github.com/pbizopoulos/a-makefile-for-developing-containerized-latex-technical-documents $HOME/github.com/pbizopoulos/a-makefile-for-developing-containerized-latex-technical-documents
cd $HOME/github.com/pbizopoulos/a-makefile-for-developing-containerized-latex-technical-documents/

# Development
cd latex/ && make clean check all && cd ..

